            <div type="transcript" id="F424A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Color of the Grave is<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Green -</l>
                    <l>The Outer Grave - I mean - </l>
                    <l>You would not know it from<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the Field - </l>
                    <l>Except it own a Stone - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To help the fond - to find it -</l>
                    <l>Too infinite asleep </l>
                    <l>To stop and tell them<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 where it is - </l>
                    <l>But just a Daisy - deep - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Color of the Grave is<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 white - </l>
                    <l>The outer Grave - I mean -</l>
                    <l>You would not know it from<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the Drifts - </l>
                    <l>In Winter - till the Sun -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Has furrowed out the Aisles - </l>
                    <l>Then - higher than the Land </l>
                    <l>The little Dwelling Houses<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 rise</l>
                    <l>Where Each - has left<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 a friend - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Color of the Grave within - </l>
                    <l>The Duplicate - I mean - </l>
                    <l>Not all the snows c'd make it white - </l>
                    <l>Not all the Summers - Green -</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>You've seen the Color - maybe - </l>
                    <l>Opon a Bonnet bound - </l>
                    <l>When that you met it with before - </l>
                    <l>The Ferret - Cannot find - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
